---
title: American BBQ Tofu & Charred Corn Bowl with Garlic Rice & Plant-Based Mayo
description: We’re stirring and cooking these little tofu cubes tonight in a lavish dark sauce. The smokiness is from the BBQ sauce and the richness is the sriracha coming together to pop against the garlic rice and charred corn. It’s decadence in a bowl.
